{
  "version": 2,
  "_doc": "Synthetic fixture set for the file-deleted-upstream branch of the excel-activities/read-range-file-not-found playbook. Agent must chain: folders list-current-user → jobs list --state Faulted → jobs get → jobs logs → jobs list (broader; reveals multiple prior Successful runs against the same process/path) → workflow source. The recent-success pattern is decisive: stable absolute path + recent successes rule out config issues; the current FileNotFoundException points at upstream deletion between runs.",
